\"ngram\": \"a major role\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"her preparation\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old athlete made history on Tuesday whenshe became the most decorated American gymnast, after the women's US gymnastics team scored gold during the all-around finals.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999957476765674, \"rank\": 4.07644292092794e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999261523014241, \"rank\": 7.362283204775857e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 27-year-old athlete\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"whenshe\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around finals\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory marked a comeback for Biles, who hadwithdrawn from the Tokyo 2020 Olympicsdue to her mental health.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The victory\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"a comeback\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicsdue\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to reporters on Tuesday after Team USA's stunning performance, Biles detailed the positive impact that going to therapy right before the competition had on her gold medal-winning performance.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9998778344119827, \"rank\": 0.00011937451879633961, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the positive impact\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"her gold medal-winning performance\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the beginning of the day, I started off with therapy this morning so that was super exciting.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I told her I was feeling calm and ready,\\\" Biles told reporters in Paris, according toCNN.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999295142, \"rank\": 7.053219414010445e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"toCNN\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And that's kind of exactly what happened.\\\"\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After I finished vault, I was relieved.\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like: 'Wooo, because please, no flashbacks or anything,'\\\" Biles recalled.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no flashbacks\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I did feel a lot of relief.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"relief\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as soon as I landed vault, I was like: 'Oh, yeah, I am definitely [okay], we are gonna do this.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before she arrived in France for this year's summer Olympics, Biles also spoke withTodayco-anchor Hoda Kotb about the importance of incorporating therapy into her daily routine.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9017312357246436, \"rank\": 0.07323178481338692, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this year's summer Olympics\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"her daily routine\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not bury things anymore.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You speak them out loud.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You talk about therapy, where you are, where you are going.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tell me about this part of you,\\\" Kotb said during an episode of her podcast,Making Space with Hoda Kotb, released on July 31.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this part\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"Kotb\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"an episode\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"her podcast\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"Space\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always tried to stay authentic to myself, so I feel like the new me, I am a little bit older, more mature, so just being unapologetically me,\\\" the gymnast said.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new me\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnast\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb then explained how many people tend to bury their feelings in order to \\\"appear stronger,\\\" which is ultimately \\\"the worst idea.\\\"\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kotb\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"how many people\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"their feelings\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst idea\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she asked if Biles felt different now that she's been open with her mental health journey, the Olympian replied: \\\"I feel a lot more free, especially going to therapy and doing those sessions so that physically and mentally I feel better, and I know that's an important part of my routine.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.99999999820011, \"rank\": 1.8000028573212963e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health journey\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"those sessions\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"my routine\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So just staying on top of that, it lightens the load a lot.\\\"\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"the load\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The professional athlete went on to credit therapy ashelping her overcome her \\\"trauma,\\\"most notably afterpublicly revealing she was sexually abusedby Team USA's former gymnastics doctor Larry Nassar.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2744, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9998778344119827, \"rank\": 0.00011937451879633961, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2780, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9965595582055985, \"rank\": 0.003452319298080305, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The professional athlete\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"credit therapy\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, Nassar wassentenced to 40 to 175 years in prisonafter pleading guilty to seven counts of first-degree criminal sexual conduct and possession of child pornography.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2803, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.739840299757683e-38, \"text\": \"Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"40 to 175 years\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"prisonafter\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"seven counts\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"first-degree criminal sexual conduct\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"possession\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2943}, {\"ngram\": \"child pornography\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think, before, I was pushing down my trauma, and now I have learned to speak on it and kind of release that,\\\" Biles said during the podcast, before adding: \\\"I think we used to think of therapy as a weakness, and now I think of it as a strength.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my trauma\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of release\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"the podcast\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"a weakness\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"a strength\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if there is somebody that can help me deal with what I am going through, then that's what I need to do.\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now it's a daily part of my routine.\\\"\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a daily part\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3349}, {\"ngram\": \"my routine\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, Bilespulled out of the women's all-around gymnastics competitionat the Tokyo Olympics to focus on her mental health, after suffering from acondition known as the \\\"twisties\\\".\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's all-around gymnastics competitionat\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3491}, {\"ngram\": \"acondition\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"twisties\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The phenomenon, typically experienced by gymnasts, involves losing control mid-air and feeling unable to land the move, creating a high-risk and dangerous situation.\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The phenomenon\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3564}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"the move\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-risk and dangerous situation\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has previously described the twisties as being \\\"lost in the air,\\\" likening the uncomfortable experience to being unable to drive while at the wheel in a car.\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3721}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3759}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"the uncomfortable experience\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3825}, {\"ngram\": \"the wheel\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"a car\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to Biles, Team USA gymnasts Jordan Chiles, Suni Lee, Hezly Rivera, and Jade Carey posed for cameras at the Bercy Arena with their gold medals.\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 4035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3921, \"end\": 3934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 3936, 